(HBO/AP) See more galleries Emilia Clarke goes by many names on HBO's "Game of Thrones": Daenerys Targaryen, Khaleesi, Mother of Dragons, The unburnt. Now she can add " Sexiest Woman Alive " to that list, thanks to Esquire Magazine.
